 Brief Introduction of French and Francophone Countries
✅ What is French?
French (le français) is a Romance language spoken on five continents.

It is one of the official languages of the United Nations, European Union, and Olympics.

🌍 Francophone Countries (Countries where French is spoken):
France 🇫🇷

Belgium 🇧🇪

Switzerland 🇨🇭

Canada (Quebec) 🇨🇦

Senegal 🇸🇳

Morocco 🇲🇦

Ivory Coast, Cameroon, Madagascar, etc.

🎯 Fun Fact:
French is spoken by over 300 million people worldwide.

